headline: Royal Caribbean Cruises (NYSE:RCL) Gains 10% Over Last Week
summary: Royal Caribbean Cruises (NYSE:RCL) experienced a significant 10% price increase over the last week, a move that may align with the broader market trend, which saw a 5% rise. While there were no major company-specific events influencing its stock price, the overall positive market sentiment, buoyed by expectations of a 14% annual earnings growth, likely contributed to this surge. headline: Barcelona Tourists Battle Water Pistols and Limits on Airbnb. Travel Firms Trudge On.
